{"tid":1082583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我食M記會特登撞跌環保撚杯汽水","createTime":"2019-03-29T05:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T17:23:59.000Z","uid":162866,"like":36,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1203ac261af7db419331419f7b4a6c10caf4c743","tid":1082583,"uid":162866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"次次去食M記都會望下邊D係唔攞飲筒既環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有環保撚打開個蓋飲汽水就會特登一野撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有次見到個後生環保撚又唔攞飲筒，襯佢開蓋飲果時一野撞埋去，淋到佢部iphone都濕埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢即刻開聲諗住屌我<br />\n<br />\n我即刻串返佢環保撚唔攞飲管係咁，怪邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇住環保撚杯汽水淋到成身都係真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n杜絕環保人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7725de263e51619b97e608fc5535111cbf7d4c80","tid":1082583,"uid":162866,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:11:05.000Z","msg":"7個環保撚負評左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4ef816708d6bef71095698167332037a1d556e","tid":1082583,"uid":4618,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"skr"},{"pid":"e032ccb73dfa081f210122ab7c4d2adfd599ddb0","tid":1082583,"uid":162866,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"又話連登反環保基地<br />\n<br />\n咁多環保撚負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj